data.description: Welcome to 1604 Wayah Drive, your new home awaits! This expansive brick-faced ranch boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 partially renovated bathrooms, and large open living areas with vaulted ceilings. The spacious floor plan provides a comfortable and welcoming atmosphere for both relaxation and entertainment. Situated on a large 0.35 acre lot in a quiet cul-de-sac that backs up to woods, this property offers both privacy and tranquility. The bonus room/4th bedroom above the garage adds versatility to the living space. The established neighborhood has tons of charm, is close 526, and has a trail that connects it directly to the West Ashley Park where you'll find ball fields, hiking trails, and a disc golf course. Don't miss the opportunity to make this new listing your home sweet home!
